snippet: The transit police officers who helped deliver a Christmas baby on a subway train reunited with the newborn boy and his parents Friday morning, trading the chaos of the dingy rail car where they first met for the comfort of a hospital room....

headline.print_headline: Officers Help Deliver Baby on Train on Christmas
headline.main: Officers Help Deliver Baby on Train on Christmas

lead_paragraph: The transit police officers who helped deliver a Christmas baby on a subway train reunited with the newborn boy and his parents Friday morning, trading the chaos of the dingy rail car where they first met for the comfort of a hospital room.
